# Load the library
library(Seurat)
library(ggplot2)
library(ggprism)
library(ggfun)
#set the color
custom_colors <- c(
  "Astrocytes" = "#ED9F9B",
  "Excitatory neurons" = "#8AB1D2",
  "Inhibitory neurons" = "#80BA8A",
  "Microglia" = "#9CD1C8",
  "MSN" = "#EEC79F",
  "Oligodendrocyte" = "#F1DFA4",
  "OPC" = "#CC88B0" ,
  "Vascular" = "#D9BDDB"
)
plant_colors_simple <- c(
  "Brain1-5 NV" = "#E58579",
  "Brain1-5 SF" = "#6BB7CA"
)
# Load the data
load("10b_2l.RData")
# Show the figure
p1 <- DimPlot(merged_10Brain, reduction = "umap", group.by = "cell_type", label = FALSE, label.size = 4)+
  scale_color_manual(values = custom_colors)+
  theme_prism(base_size = 8)+
  theme(
    axis.title = element_blank(),
    axis.text = element_blank(),
    axis.ticks = element_blank(),
    axis.line = element_blank(),
    plot.margin = margin(5, 5, 5, 5)
  )+
  NoLegend()+
  ggtitle(NULL)
merged_10Brain$platform_group <- ifelse(grepl("NV", merged_10Brain$orig.ident),
                                        "Brain1-5 NV",
                                        "Brain1-5 SF")
p2 <- DimPlot(merged_10Brain,
              reduction = "umap",
              group.by = "platform_group",
              label = FALSE) +
  scale_color_manual(values = plant_colors_simple)+  
  theme_prism(base_size = 10) +
  theme(
    axis.title = element_blank(),
    axis.text = element_blank(),
    axis.ticks = element_blank(),
    axis.line = element_blank(),
    plot.margin = margin(5, 5, 5, 5)
  )+
  guides(color = guide_legend(
    override.aes = list(size = 5),
    title.theme = element_text(size = 15, face = "bold"),
    label.theme = element_text(size = 12, face = "bold")
  ))+
  ggtitle(NULL)
p<-p1 + p2
p

Figure 2 (C)

# Load the data
cell_data <- merged_10Brain@meta.data
coords <- function(df){
  x <- df[["x"]]
  y <- df[["y"]]
  data.frame(x = x, y = y, cell_type = df[["cell_type"]])
}
filtered_data_nv <- cell_data[cell_data[["orig.ident"]] == "Brain1 NV", ]
filtered_data_sf <- cell_data[cell_data[["orig.ident"]] == "Brain1 SF", ]
plot_data_nv <- coords(filtered_data_nv)
plot_data_sf <- coords(filtered_data_sf)
# Show the figure
p1 <- ggplot(plot_data_nv, aes(x = x, y = y, color = cell_type)) +
  geom_point(size = 0.5, show.legend = TRUE) +
  theme_minimal() +
  labs(title = "Brain1 NV", color = "Cell Type") +
  coord_fixed(ratio = 1) +
  theme_prism(base_size = 20)+
  scale_color_manual(values = custom_colors) +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(size = 18, face = "bold", hjust = 0.5),
    legend.title = element_text(size = 13, face = "bold"),
    legend.text = element_text(size = 10, face = "bold"),
    axis.title = element_blank(),
    axis.text = element_blank(),
    axis.ticks = element_blank(),
    axis.line = element_blank()
  ) +
  guides(color = guide_legend(
    override.aes = list(size = 6),
    title.theme = element_text(size = 18, face = "bold"),
    label.theme = element_text(size = 18, face = "bold"),
    ncol = 2
  ))
p2 <- ggplot(plot_data_sf, aes(x = x, y = y, color = cell_type)) +
  geom_point(size = 0.5, show.legend = TRUE) +
  theme_minimal() +
  labs(title = "Brain1 SF", color = "Cell Type") +
  coord_fixed(ratio = 1) +
  theme_prism(base_size = 20)+
  scale_color_manual(values = custom_colors) +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(size = 18, face = "bold", hjust = 0.5),
    legend.title = element_text(size = 13, face = "bold"),
    axis.title = element_blank(),
    axis.text = element_blank(),
    axis.ticks = element_blank(),
    axis.line = element_blank()
  ) +
  guides(color = guide_legend(
    override.aes = list(size = 6),
    title.theme = element_text(size = 18, face = "bold"),
    label.theme = element_text(size = 18, face = "bold"),
    ncol = 2
  ))
p <- p1 / p2
p

Figure 2 (D)

# Load the library
library(MetaNeighbor)
library(dplyr)
library(tidyr)
# Load the data
sce <- as.SingleCellExperiment(merged_10Brain, assay = "SCT")
hvgs <- head(merged_10Brain@assays[["SCT"]]@var.features, 3000)
study_id <- sce@colData[["orig.ident"]]
cell_type <- sce@colData[["cell_type"]]
Aurocs_matrix <- MetaNeighborUS(
  var_genes = hvgs,
  dat = sce,
  study_id = study_id,
  cell_type = cell_type,
  fast_version = TRUE
)
auroc_df <- as.data.frame(as.table(Aurocs_matrix))
auroc_df <- auroc_df %>% 
  separate(Var1, into = c("Sample", "CellType"), sep = "\\|") %>% 
  separate(Var2, into = c("Sample_2", "CellType_2"), sep = "\\|") %>% 
  rename(AUROC = Freq)
auroc_df$Sample <- gsub(".*\\s(NV|SF)$", "\\1", auroc_df$Sample)
auroc_df$Sample_2 <- gsub(".*\\s(NV|SF)$", "\\1", auroc_df$Sample_2)
auroc_df$Sample <- factor(auroc_df$Sample, levels = c("NV", "SF"))
auroc_df$Sample_2 <- factor(auroc_df$Sample_2, levels = c("NV", "SF"))
auroc_df$CellType <- factor(auroc_df$CellType, levels = names(custom_colors))
# Show the figure
p<- ggplot(auroc_df, aes(x = Sample, y = AUROC, fill = CellType)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", position = "dodge") +
  theme_minimal() +
  labs(
    y = "AUROC"
  ) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = custom_colors) + 
  theme_prism(base_size = 22) +
  theme(
    plot.margin = margin(25, 25, 25, 25),
    axis.title.x = element_blank()
  )+
  NoLegend()
p

Figure 2 (E)

# Load the data
Idents(merged_10Brain) <- merged_10Brain@meta.data$cell_type
selected_genes <- c("Ptprb", "Ctss", "Slc1a3", "Lhfpl3", "Mbp", "Pde10a", "Gad2", "Slc17a7")
plot_data <- DotPlot(merged_10Brain, features = selected_genes)$data
celltype_order <- c(
  "Excitatory neurons", 
  "Inhibitory neurons", 
  "MSN", 
  "Oligodendrocyte", 
  "OPC", 
  "Astrocytes", 
  "Microglia",
  "Vascular"
)
plot_data$id <- factor(plot_data$id, levels = celltype_order)
plot_data$combined_score <- plot_data$avg.exp.scaled * (plot_data$pct.exp/100)
# Show the figure
ggplot(plot_data, aes(x = features.plot, y = id, 
                      size = combined_score, 
                      color = avg.exp.scaled)) +
    geom_point() +
    scale_size_continuous(range = c(2, 15)) +
    scale_color_gradient(low = "#FFFFFF", 
                        high = "#AD1C42",    
                        breaks = c(0, max(plot_data$avg.exp.scaled)/2, max(plot_data$avg.exp.scaled)),
                        labels = function(x) sprintf("%.1f", x)) +
    theme_minimal() +
    theme(
        axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 30,    
                                 hjust = 1,
                                 size = 26,        
                                 face = "bold",
                                 color = "#333333"),  
        axis.text.y = element_text(size = 26,     
                                 face = "bold",
                                 color = "#333333"),  
        legend.text = element_text(size = 22,     
                                 face = "bold",
                                 color = "#333333"),  
        legend.title = element_text(size = 24,    
                                  face = "bold",
                                  color = "#333333"),  
        axis.title = element_blank(),
        legend.position = "bottom",
        plot.margin = unit(c(0.8, 2, 1.2, 2), "cm"),
        panel.grid.major = element_line(color = "grey90"),
        panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
        legend.spacing.x = unit(1, 'cm'),
        legend.box.margin = margin(-10, -300, 0, -300)
    ) +
    coord_flip() +
    guides(
        size = guide_legend(title = "Expression Score",
                           title.position = "top",
                           title.hjust = 0.5,
                           nrow = 1),
        color = guide_colorbar(title = "Scaled Expression",
                             title.position = "top",
                             title.hjust = 0.5,
                             barwidth = 15,
                             barheight = 1,
                             nrow = 1,
                             ticks.linewidth = 1,
                             label.theme = element_text(size = 20,    
                                                      face = "bold",
                                                      color = "#333333"))  
    )
